          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "اَلرَّجُلِ يَنْزِلُ عَلَى اَلرَّجُلِ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " وَ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "لَهُ عَلَيْهِ دَيْنٌ أَ يَأْكُلُ مِنْ طَعَامِهِ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " فَقَالَ"
          }
        ]
      },
      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:3:2:12:27",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/2/2/27",
      "text": [
        " \"نَعَمْ يَأْكُلُ مِنْ طَعَامِهِ ثَلاَثَةَ أَيَّامٍ وَ لاَ يَأْكُلُ بَعْدَ ذَلِكَ شَيْئاً\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3705 - Sama'ah asked Abu Abdillah (as) about a man who stays with another man to whom he owes a debt. Is it permissible for him to eat from his food?\nImam (as) said: \"Yes, he may eat from his food for three days, but after that, he should not eat anything.\""
        ]
      }
    },
